  {"type":"rectangle","id":"tech-comments","x":60,"y":600,"width":1100,"height":300,"strokeColor":"#455a64","strokeWidth":1,"fillStyle":"dashed","backgroundColor":"#eceff1","roughness":0,"roundness":{"type":3},"boundElements":[{"type":"text","id":"tech-comments-text"}]},
  {"type":"text","id":"tech-comments-text","x":70,"y":610,"width":1080,"height":280,"fontSize":11,"fontFamily":1,"text":"Technical Details:\n\nSearch Flow (GET /api/circulars/search):\n1. Flask API validates query + strategy (bm25|vector|hybrid)\n2. get_es_client().search(query, metadata, strategy) called\n3. For hybrid: BM25 query and KNN query run in parallel (size=40 each via ES_RRF_WINDOW_SIZE=50)\n4. Each query gets top 50 results; results converted to ranx.Run objects {query_id: {doc_id: score}}\n5. ranx.rrf([bm25_run, knn_run], k=60) fuses ranked lists using RRF formula: 1/(60+rank)\n6. Fused results sorted descending, limited to size=40\n7. SearchHit list returned (for hybrid/vector: passed to RAGAnswerGenerator)\n\nPreview Generation (SearchHit.build_preview):\n1. multi_snippet(text, query, window_size=120, merge_gap=80, max_snippets=3)\n2. Keywords extracted from query, windows created around each match\n3. Windows sorted by position, merged if overlapping or within merge_gap\n4. Broken words stripped at edges, ellipsis prefix/suffix added\n5. highlight(snippet, query) wraps query terms in <mark> tags via regex\n6. Returns: <div class='preview'>...highlighted snippets...</div>\n\nRAG Answer Generation (strategy=hybrid|vector):\n1. Limited to top 10 hits (RAG_MAX_CHUNKS)\n2. _build_context_chunks() extracts: circular_id, title, source, url, full_reference, chunk_text, score\n3. _build_prompt() creates formatted context with circular headers\n4. LLM chat.completions.create(model=minimax-m2.7, response_model=RAGAnswer, messages=[...])\n5. Returns RAGAnswer: answer (str), references (list[Citation]), snippets (list[str])\n6. If LLM fails: fallback returns raw results with rag_error field\n\nAPI Response Structure:\n• strategy=bm25: {query, strategy, results: [{id, score, preview, document}]}\n• strategy=hybrid|vector: {query, strategy, answer, references, snippets}\n• On RAG failure: {query, strategy, results, rag_error}\n\nConfiguration (config.py):\n• ES_QUERY_EMBEDDING_INSTRUCTION: \"Represent this sentence for searching relevant passages: \"\n• ES_RRF_WINDOW_SIZE=50, ES_RRF_RANK_CONSTANT=60 (ranx library)\n• RAG_MODEL=minimaxai/minimax-m2.7, RAG_MAX_CHUNKS=10, RAG_MAX_TOKENS=4000\n• ES_SEARCH_DEFAULT_STRATEGY=hybrid\n• NVIDIA_API_KEY via environment variable\n• ELASTICSEARCH_URL=http://localhost:9200, ES_REQUEST_TIMEOUT_SECONDS=30", "textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","baseline":160,"containerId":"tech-comments","roughness":0,"roundness":null,"strokeStyle":"solid"}
],"files":{},"appState":{"gridSize":null,"viewBackgroundColor":"#ffffff"}}
